author: The Capital-Journal
title: PrepZone Podcast: Discussing the new district assignments
text:
By The Capital-Journal 
The Topeka Capital-Journal's Rick Peterson and Brent Maycock join Pat Strathman of 580 WIBW and Chris Lilly of WIBW-TV for this week's edition of the Capital City Prep Zone Podcast. 
This week, the crew discuss the new district assignments for football in 2016-17 and the renewal of the Hayden-Holton rivalry, also predicting winners for this week's city prep football action. 
Mobile users, click here to listen to this week's podcast.
